# Files consumed by Docker / Linux must stay LF. With core.autocrlf=true they
# would otherwise check out as CRLF on Windows, and a CR after a backslash line
# continuation in the Dockerfile RUN steps breaks the build on Linux.
Dockerfile text eol=lf
.dockerignore text eol=lf
docker-compose.yml text eol=lf
docs/HOSTING.md text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
